No. 09-7853. Dennis H. Wendell, Petitioner v. United States District Court for the Northern District of New York. 559 U.S. 963, 130 S. Ct. 1570,

176 L. Ed. 2d 152,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 1053, February 22, 2010.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied.

Justice Sotomayor took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
